{"tid":129434,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有時和朋友愈閒聊愈深入, 就覺得生不逢時","createTime":"2017-02-21T14:48:30.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-22T10:34:19.000Z","uid":34286,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b58e9405d0d3d9117c0a8881a0eacb6686a5c31f","tid":129434,"uid":34286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T14:48:30.000Z","msg":"有時和朋友愈閒聊愈深入, 就覺得生不逢時<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n看見東莞個post, 真心覺得生不逢時<br />\n<br />\n香港經濟起飛那30年:<br />\n<br />\n香港人身份又威, 番強國做大爺, 當年可以大把靚女揀<br />\n當年考正苦工, 考個督察也相當容易<br />\n當年30歲未有樓是你失敗<br />\n當年30歲做到經理比比皆是<br />\n人工升幅遠遠大於通漲<br />\n當年整個社會是開心的, 氣氛是相當好的<br />\n當年正苦工是被認為失敗才做的工作<br />\n就算講移民, 當年也很容易, 不像現在門檻那麼高<br />\n當年90年代初樓價等同沙士時, 但平均工資遠遠比沙士時高<br />\n當年機會處處<br />\n當年香港就是一個名牌<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac946b12f4bec0d1eabb7417942a701d244d471b","tid":129434,"uid":2247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T14:57:11.000Z","msg":"喂 果陣易買樓都冇能力買？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n有時d野唔係整定架 要怪就怪你屋企有能力改變既時候唔敢搏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c91e6a34cdfd826911e99867651332972d48a2bd","tid":129434,"uid":9136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T15:10:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>喂 果陣易買樓都冇能力買？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n有時d野唔係整定架 要怪就怪你屋企有能力改變既時候唔敢搏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n無錯, 整定, 有D二世祖就係當時佢地父母肯博"},{"pid":"0a7946c46c3df0b679b56f929c9e2472f31463a6","tid":129434,"uid":2247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T15:13:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>喂 果陣易買樓都冇能力買？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"h